title: Man United boss Jose Mourinho storms off during interview after Hull draw
text:
Man   storms off during interview after Hull draw JOSE MOURINHO stormed after mid-way through an interview after Manchester United's game against Hull. PUBLISHED: 22:12,  20,   Jose Mourinho was annoyed with the referee's display against Hull 
The Manchester United boss was furious after the goalless draw against the Tigers earlier this evening. 
United saw some chances come and go, but Mourinho apparently wasn't pleased with how the referee Lee Mason fared during the game. 
More to follow
